text: National Highway 361B, commonly referred to as NH 361B, is a national highway in India. It is a spur road of National Highway 61. NH-361B traverses the state of Maharashtra in India. == Route == Kalamb - Ralegaon - Kapsi - Sirasgaon - Vadner - Wadki. == Junctions == : Terminal near Kalamb. : Terminal near Wadki. == See also == * List of National Highways in India * List of National Highways in India by state == References == == External links == * NH 361B on OpenStreetMap Category:National highways in India Category:National Highways in Maharashtra
